description: Excludes gift card purchases, up to a maximum discount of $20
terms: Offer valid for one time usage on regular, sale and promotional merchandise at any Garage or Dynamite store in Canada or the USA, on the in-store e-comm tablet or on Garage.ca or Dynamiteclothing.com or on the Garage or Dynamite app. No minimum spend required. Cannot be used on previous purchases or towards the purchase of gift cards, e-gift cards, the sale of charitable merchandise or donations. Garage/Dynamite is not responsible for lost or stolen coupons.
